long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This app will help safemoon owners to check the price of it in real time. She also redirect to the website for more features. This extension uses the dex.guru API in order to have the prices closest to reality. No personal data is required to use this application. 
This application therefore makes it possible to check the value of the Safemoon without having to go to several sites.
